         <div class="documentTop SubjectPage">            
                     
            <h1>Culture, leisure and belief systems</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/kultur_fritid_livssyn_150x1.jpg" alt="Smiling faces" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The arts, culture and the voluntary sector contribute to a richer society. Through specific measures and a general strengthening of the arts, culture and the voluntary sector, the Government aims to improve the situation of the cultural and voluntary sectors. Freedom of belief and religion are fundamental values which society and the law must strengthen and protect.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/kultur_fritid_livssyn_150x1.jpg" alt="Smiling faces" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p><em>The Ministry of Culture and Church Affairs</em> is responsible for culture, the church, media, sport and the gaming and lottery sector. The Ministry is also responsible for coordinating government policy in relation to the voluntary sector.&nbsp; </p>
<p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to culture, leisure and belief systems. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p></div>
